		<div id="main">




<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" title="academic programs" src="/images/Academic.jpg" alt="academic programs" width="484" height="144" /></p>

<p>Interdisciplinary research and collaboration are hallmarks of the Bourns College of Engineering. We also are distinguished by our teaching. Faculty inspire, teach and challenge our students, engaging them in hands-on research and multifaceted design programs that involve real-world problems.</p>
<p>Our fully accredited programs offer the B.S., M.S. and Ph.D. degrees in a range of disciplines.&nbsp;Our five-year joint B.S.+ M.S. program allows top-performing students to prepare for careers in diverse industries on an accelerated schedule. Our new Materials Science and Engineering Program crosses the boundaries of all the engineering disciplines as well as those in the College of Natural and Agricultural Sciences.</p>
<h3>Departments and Programs&nbsp;</h3>
<h6><a style="font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.5em;" title="bioengineering department" href="http://www.bioeng.ucr.edu/" target="_blank"><img class="img_L" title="bioengineering department" src="/images/bienlink.jpg" alt="bioengineering department" width="150" height="45" /></a></h6>
<p><a title="chemical environmental engineering" href="http://www.cee.ucr.edu/" target="_blank"><img class="img_L" title="chemical environmental engineering" src="/images/ChemicalEng4.jpg" alt="chemical environmental engineering" width="150" height="45" /></a> <a title="computer engineering" href="http://cen.ucr.edu/" target="_blank"><img class="img_L" title="computer engineering" src="/images/celink.jpg" alt="computer engineering" width="150" height="45" /></a> <a title="computer science engineering" href="http://www1.cs.ucr.edu/" target="_blank"><img class="img_L" title="computer science engineering" src="/images/cselink.jpg" alt="computer science engineering" width="150" height="45" /></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href="http://www.bioeng.ucr.edu/"> BIEN website</a> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href="http://www.cee.ucr.edu/">CEE website </a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href="http://cen.ucr.edu/">CE website</a> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href="http://www1.cs.ucr.edu/">CSE website</a></p>
<p><a title="electrical engineering" href="http://www.ee.ucr.edu/" target="_blank"><img class="img_L" title="electrical engineering" src="/images/ECE%20button.jpg" alt="electrical engineering" width="150" height="45" /></a></p>
<p><a title="materials science engineering" href="http://cmsmse.engr.ucr.edu" target="_blank"><img class="img_L" title="materials science engineering" src="/images/mselink.jpg" alt="materials science engineering" width="150" height="45" /></a></p>
<p><a title="mechanical engineering" href="http://www.me.ucr.edu/" target="_blank"><img class="img_L" title="mechanical engineering" src="/images/melink.jpg" alt="mechanical engineering" width="150" height="45" /></a> <a title="online MS in Engineering" href="http://www.msol.ucr.edu/" target="_blank"><img class="img_L" title="Online MS in Engineering" src="/images/msols.jpg" alt="Online MS in Engineering" width="150" height="45" /></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href="http://www.ee.ucr.edu/">ECE website</a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href="http://cmsmse.engr.ucr.edu">MSE website</a> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href="http://www.me.ucr.edu/">ME website</a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href="http://www.msol.ucr.edu/">MSOL website</a></p>
<div class="clear"></div>
<h3 class="section2">Undergraduate Degrees and Majors*</h3>
<ul>
<li>B.S. in Bioengineering</li>
<li>B.S.+ M.S. in Chemical and Environmental Engineering</li>
<li>B.S. in Chemical Engineering (four concentrations)
<ul>
<li><em>Bioengineering</em></li>
<li><em>Biochemical Engineering</em></li>
<li><em>Chemical Engineering</em></li>
<li><em>Nanotechnology</em></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>B.S.+ M.S. in Computer Science and Engineering</li>
<li>B.S. in Computer Engineering</li>
<li>B.S. in Computer Science</li>
<li>B.S.+ M.S. in Electrical Engineering</li>
<li>B.S. in Electrical Engineering</li>
<li>B.S. in Environmental Engineering (two concentrations)
<ul>
<li><em>Air Pollution Control</em></li>
<li><em>Water Pollution Control</em></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>B.S. in Business Informatics (offered jointly with the A. Gary Anderson Graduate School of Management)</li>
<li>B.S. in Materials Science and Engineering</li>
<li>B.S.+ M.S. in Mechanical Engineering</li>
<li>B.S. in Mechanical Engineering (four concentrations)
<ul>
<li><em>Materials and Structures</em></li>
<li><em>Energy and Environment</em></li>
<li><em>Design and Manufacturing</em></li>
<li><em>General Mechanical Engineering</em></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p><em>*Concentrations are in italics.</em></p>
<h3 class="section2">Graduate Degrees</h3>
<ul>
<li>M.S. in Bioengineering</li>
<li>M.S. in Chemical &amp; Environmental Engineering</li>
<li>M.S. in Computer Science</li>
<li>M.S. in Electrical Engineering</li>
<li>M.S. in Computer Engineering</li>
<li>M.S. in Engineering (online)</li>
<li>M.S. in Mechanical Engineering</li>
<li>M.S. in Materials Science and Engineering</li>
</ul>
<br />
<ul>
<li>Ph.D. in Bioengineering</li>
<li>Ph.D. in Chemical &amp; Environmental Engineering</li>
<li>Ph.D. in Computer Science</li>
<li>Ph.D. in Electrical Engineering</li>
<li>Ph.D. in Materials Science and Engineering</li>
<li>Ph.D. in Mechanical Engineering</li>
</ul>

